{"data": [{"id": "4741814", "title": "AMD: Positioned For Takeoff As 2025 Demand Gains Momentum", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract circuit board with a lot of micro chips\" data-id=\"1397047849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sankai</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The recent pullback in <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) stock following its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4220849-advanced-micro-devices-non-gaap-eps-of-0_92-in-line-revenue-of-6_82m-misses-6_7b\">Q3 2024 earnings report</a> presents what, I believe, is a Dip-Buy opportunity for long-term investors. Because of AMD's accelerating momentum in the artificial intelligence and data</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741814-amd-positioned-for-takeoff-as-2025-demand-gains-momentum", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:32:32"}, {"id": "4741837", "title": "Singapore Banks Expect Wealth Management, Loans To Drive Earnings Momentum", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Singapore flag waving in the wind against background of peoples park old building\" data-id=\"1263355177\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3333px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kandl</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Singapore's three largest banks expect wealth management and growing loan portfolios to drive earnings in 2025 after they posted strong earnings growth in the third quarter.</p> <p>DBS Group Holdings Ltd. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DBSDF\" title=\"DBS Group Holdings Ltd\">OTCPK:DBSDF</a>) reported net income of S$3.03 billion</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741837-singapore-banks-expect-wealth-management-loans-to-drive-earnings-momentum", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:28:00"}, {"id": "4741809", "title": "EVgo: Q3 Results Likely To Support Reversal Rally", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young Asian woman uses her smartphone to make contactless payment after charging her car at an electric vehicle (&lt;a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EV' title=''&gt;EV&lt;/a&gt;) charging station\" data-id=\"2159031349\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Initiating Coverage</h2> <p>I am initiating coverage on <strong>EVgo, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EVGO\" title=\"EVgo, Inc.\">EVGO</a></span>) with a \"<em>Buy</em>\" rating and an investment horizon of 24 months. I believe that EVgo is among the best</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741809-evgo-stock-q3-results-likely-to-support-reversal-rally", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:14:53"}, {"id": "4741829", "title": "Australian Banks Rely On Capital To Offset Margin Pressures, Profit Declines", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Random little white piggy banks\" data-id=\"1072593766\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5174px\" height=\"3454px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Australia's biggest banks demonstrated resilience in their financial results for the recently concluded fiscal year, reflecting robust capital levels amid intense competition.</p> <p>The country's four major lenders reported a decline in their net profits for the fiscal</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741829-australian-banks-rely-on-capital-offset-margin-pressures-profit-declines", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:09:00"}, {"id": "4741830", "title": "UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Stanley Black &amp; Decker, Inc. in conjunction with this event.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106009\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741830-ubs-global-industrials-and-transportation-conference", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:05:18"}, {"id": "4741817", "title": "Total Return Forecasts: Major Asset Classes - December 3, 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman is stacking coins\" data-id=\"183865137\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1006px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">acilo</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The long-term performance forecast for the Global Market Index (GMI) continued to increase in November, marking a full reversal of the recent slide in ex ante data. Today\u2019s estimate also marks the highest return outlook in recent history and is modestly above</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183865137/image_183865137.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741817-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-december-3-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:00:00"}, {"id": "4741801", "title": "Energias de Portugal: Still Left Behind", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ribeira dilhas beach in Ericeira with turquoise water on a sunny day, in Portugal\" data-id=\"1384018244\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">LuisPinaPhotogrpahy/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Energias de Portugal, or EDP S.A. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EDPFY\" title=\"EDP, S.A.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:EDPFY</a>), remains our preferred utilities pick in Europe, and with the recent pullback in price it continues to be relatively undervalued as we commented in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4689000-energias-de-portugal-focus-deleveraging-could-benefit-stock-price\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4689000-energias-de-portugal-focus-deleveraging-could-benefit-stock-price\" target=\"_blank\">our last article</a>. We do think some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384018244/image_1384018244.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741801-energias-de-portugal-still-left-behind", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:55:27"}, {"id": "4741819", "title": "Leverage And Speculation Are At Extremes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Currency and Exchange Stock Chart for Finance and Economy Display\" data-id=\"1358927461\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cemagraphics</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Financial markets often move in cycles where enthusiasm drives prices higher, sometimes far beyond what fundamentals justify. As discussed in last week\u2019s <strong><em><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741307-extreme-speculation-has-returned\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener noopener noopener\">#BullBearReport</a></em></strong>, leverage and speculation are at the heart of many such cycles. These two powerful forces support</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741819-leverage-speculation-at-extremes", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:46:00"}, {"id": "4741812", "title": "Core & Main, Inc. 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Core &amp; Main, Inc. in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106008\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741812-core-and-main-inc-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:32:01"}, {"id": "4741794", "title": "Lindblad Expeditions: Upbeat Earnings Momentum, But A Moderate Overvaluation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148329826/image_148329826.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Overview of large cruise ship sailing through icy waters\" data-id=\"148329826\" data-type=\"getty-image\" widt